accident.confirm_body:
AeroACARS detected strong indicators of an accident:

{{reasons}}

If correct, the flight will be filed as accident/review with score 0. If not, you can still file it as a hard landing.

active_flight.confirm_cancel_after_file_failed_body:
The auto-file attempt did not succeed:

{{reason}}

You can fix the issue and try filing again, or explicitly discard the PIREP now. Discarding deletes the PIREP — the flown route will be lost.
